About Me

Hi, I'm Sumit Ghugare, an aspiring full-stack developer with a solid foundation in computer science. My journey began with a Diploma in Computer Engineering, and I'm currently pursuing a BTech in Computer Science from M.S. Bidve Engineering College, Latur.

I specialize in MERN stack development, and I'm passionate about building impactful, scalable, and secure web applications. I enjoy learning new technologies and applying them to real-world projects.

With experience in frontend technologies like React.js and Next.js, backend frameworks including Node.js and Express, and various databases, I strive to create elegant solutions to complex problems.
